                            <comment id="15053428" author="pascalschumacher" created="Fri, 11 Dec 2015 19:38:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Just adding a != null check for the detail was not possible, because it is used to determine the class of the exception created. I solved this be creating a generic SOAPFaultException when the detail is not present.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
